-- Cherop of Kenya Wins Women’s Championship in Boston Marathon
-- B y   E b e n   N o v y - W i l l i a m s
-- 2012-04-16T16:07:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-16/cherop-of-kenya-wins-women-s-championship-in-boston-marathon.html
Sharon Cherop of  Kenya  pulled away
with 600 meters to go, then held off Jemima Sumgong by two
seconds to win the women’s championship in the Boston Marathon.  Cherop’s unofficial time was 2 hours, 31 minutes, 50
seconds on a day with record-high temperatures in the forecast.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Larry Siddons at 
 lsiddons@bloomberg.net  